Description: A simple regression testing framework for LFE.


Compile with:
     erl -noshell -pa $WORK_PATH -pa $LFE_PATH \
         -eval 'code:load_file(demo).' \
         -eval 'io:format("~n~p~n",[demo:start()]).' -s erlang halt

Run test with: 
     erl -noshell -pa $WORK_PATH -pa $LFE_PATH \
         -eval 'code:load_file(demo).' \
         -eval 'io:format("~n~p~n",[demo:start()]).' -s erlang halt




